depending on which computer it is being run on

Version 2 November 96
Works on A3000,A4000 and A5000 from same code for
all versions
Totaly revamped front end including which screen to
start from
New screen renderer

Version 3 April/May/June 97
V3.00  8/6/97
Totally new (multi-tasking) screen designer
Totally re-written, configurable, multi-tasking 
version
V3.01 3/1/99
Fixed bug in colour translation table for sprites
that prevented the title screen being shown correctly
(sometimes not at all) in screen modes with more than
256 colours
Added option to turn animation off in title (choose
version) screen, as with textured window backgrounds
the texture was lost where the sprite had been
V3.02 11/1/99
Rewrote handling of instructions so they could be
changed when you edit a level, as previously they were
a bit of a kludge, being hardwired into the code